#
# 1. To add more reviewers, append GitHub usernames with @ prefix
#    Example: /scanners/*.py @dondada876 @reviewer2
#
# 2. For team-based reviews, use @org/team-name
#    Example: /scanners/*.py @dondada876 @myorg/security-team
#
# 3. CODEOWNERS rules are enforced when:
#    - Branch protection is enabled
#    - "Require review from Code Owners" is checked in branch settings
#
# 4. To bypass CODEOWNERS (emergency only):
#    - Admin override capability must be enabled
#    - Document reason in PR description
#    - Create follow-up issue for review
